{"tid":1697464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位停止襲擊何妖嘅新聞討論","createTime":"2019-11-07T01:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T06:21:09.000Z","uid":47496,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a794d3bb128b538f44156d25656c7b4273ba9909","tid":1697464,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:18:20.000Z","msg":"而家不斷咁講呢單新聞就中哂中央嘅計<br />\n從政府、黨媒、中央政府嘅回應真係太過快<br />\n好似早有預謀咁<br />\n仲要何妖喺聲明度抹黑示威者做<br />\n自己就成為受害者<br />\n政府都冇因為因趙家賢被咬甩耳仔而有咁有嘅feedback<br />\n呢個明顯係一個局幫何妖洗白同爭取選票<br />\n由得呢單新聞沉落去<br />\n一冇討論價值就冇人會拎返出嚟講<br />\n最緊要係唔討論就等於唔幫何妖宣傳<br />\n希望各位理解！"},{"pid":"40dfbc29a6334093a0628db63416b33490ec0711","tid":1697464,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af19130de4687b29bf7580ba539e0b559ab66e82","tid":1697464,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:23:37.000Z","msg":"無視自製假新聞 <br />\n繼續討論未來行動"},{"pid":"c61cb62e50d861a793fa2d01b4323eac06a45a10","tid":1697464,"uid":102550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"話知何妖死"},{"pid":"f88b6d1229e37653caa734689e99c41565fcba16","tid":1697464,"uid":25108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"起身成版都係何妖<br />\n又係度搶住認頭,又話人割<br />\n真係幾明顯下<br />\n上次割頸又係咁"},{"pid":"d28857769258009acb0f5102387c06336ad01ee2","tid":1697464,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257b2b47702eb7bd8cbbfea8a73177f25008e38b","tid":1697464,"uid":139474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af19130de4687b29bf7580ba539e0b559ab66e82","tid":1697464,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:23:37.000Z","msg":"無視自製假新聞 <br />\n繼續討論未來行動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"